title: Labor Party of Liberia
text:
The Labor Party of Liberia (LPL) is a <a href="political%20party">political party</a> in <a href="Liberia">Liberia</a>. It fielded candidates in the 11 October 2005 <a href="Liberia%20elections%2C%202005">elections</a>.
LPL candidate <a href="Joseph%20Woah-Tee">Joseph Woah-Tee</a> won 0.6% of the vote in the presidential poll. The party failed to win any seats in the <a href="Senate%20of%20Liberia">Senate</a> or <a href="House%20of%20Representatives%20of%20Liberia">House of Representatives</a>.
